{"tid":990363,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【東京血拼攻略】33歲沈韋汝係金牌主持　未婚產子有富商生父照顧","createTime":"2019-01-21T13:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T15:47:35.000Z","uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6bdf24fe8d9d53d87b36149402de87249db0d5c6","tid":990363,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:43:08.000Z","msg":"《東京血拼攻略》於周日（1月20日）播出，有收看的都應該留意到，節目中除有2位2本地代表吳若希（Jinny）及林穎彤（Bella）之外，還有兩位來自台灣的靚女主持。可以是基於香港人對台灣的好感，有不少人大讚Bella夠可愛之餘，更多的是討論台灣主持沈韋汝。<br />\n<br />\n沈韋汝在台灣其實都算是有些知名度的藝人，自2005年起，就入行為中天娛樂台的節目《小氣大財神》擔任助理主持，而她亦有份擔任2017年台灣旅遊節目《愛玩客》，2018年TVB J2台《就是愛美麗》其實也有她的出現。當然，這位台灣女生還客片了大大小小的節目、電視劇集，以及廣告雜誌等等。不過，網民的討論焦點還是在她與年齡不相符的樣貌身材，以及愛情生活。<br />\n<br />\n原來有暱稱「小天使」的沈韋汝，現年已是33歲，並已是一子之母。據台灣「ETtoday」報導，她在2010年與台灣遠東航空董事長張綱維熱戀，同年更未婚生子，不過由此至終並未登記註冊結婚，及後因韋汝發展男方與自家公司空姐約會，因而憤而提出分手。不過時隔多年，女方態度似乎明顯軟化，她和兒子的爸爸張綱維，近年都會相聚食飯，男方更會固定給她每月15萬台幣元生活費作為對韋汝母子的照顧。沈韋汝對此還直認不瑋，母子兩人一直受男方照顧，孩子家長會以及重要節日也一起渡過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMjP83D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMjP83D.png&h=1312cc79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BpHihW0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBpHihW0.png&h=7e38a1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BuQWO3H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBuQWO3H.png&h=5b01e7ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFxBO3J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFxBO3J.png&h=2e1989b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CC7983L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCC7983L.png&h=3480d0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUMV4B7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUMV4B7.png&h=4420b290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dfaot3P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDfaot3P.png&h=13c3a905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EkThyvv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEkThyvv.png&h=32b3dab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxkDhXb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxkDhXb.png&h=98b236c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c20a40173a1e4eedf68fae6764e8fb6abd3453a3","tid":990363,"uid":78429,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"後因韋汝發展男方與自家公司空姐約會，因而憤而提出分手<br />\n<br />\n條仔當佢係雞咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98cbd1094e734aeb84f6ef9bdc98fa9e2dcb396","tid":990363,"uid":8042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"有啲似西西西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536c8ad55a185fe8b80f67a63773777164dbbf86","tid":990363,"uid":87272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:38:36.000Z","msg":"想俾佢養"},{"pid":"61b749223f3c764c54f9a821da03eda5cae2dcf1","tid":990363,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:42:23.000Z","msg":"小氣大財神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7374f8f54a88db20fd2499d34670041e820604af","tid":990363,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"生過應該幾好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}